# Keep build contexts small and deterministic.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/bin
**/obj
**/.vite
**/.turbo
# Stale tsc -b incremental state would make `tsc -b` skip emitting dist on a
# fresh build context — exclude it so Docker always does a clean compile.
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.tmp
data/generated/*
data/cache/*
data/map-packages/*
!**/.gitkeep
.git
*.md
vault/
docs/
